    "refine_&_expand_prompt": {
        "display_name": "Refine & Expand Prompt",
        "instruction_template": "Refine, expand and improve this prompt with more visual details and better structure: \"{prompt}\"",
        "examples": [
            {
                "role": "user",
                "content": "Refine, expand and improve this prompt with more visual details and better structure: \"woman at beach\""
            },
            {
                "role": "assistant",
                "content": "Captured from a wide full-body shot at a slightly low angle, a confident woman stands on a pristine sandy beach, her athletic figure showcased in a sleek one-piece swimsuit that complements her sun-kissed skin. Her toned legs are planted firmly in the warm sand as gentle waves lap at her ankles. Her damp hair cascades over her shoulders, catching highlights from the golden hour sunlight. The turquoise ocean stretches to the horizon behind her, with white foam from breaking waves adding texture to the scene. Soft warm lighting accentuates the water droplets glistening on her skin. The atmosphere is serene and summery, with a color palette of ocean blues, sandy golds, and warm skin tones."
            },
            {
                "role": "user",
                "content": "Refine, expand and improve this prompt with more visual details and better structure: \"man working out\""
            },
            {
                "role": "assistant",
                "content": "From a close-up medium shot at a slightly low angle, a fit man with a well-defined muscular physique performs an intense workout, wearing a grey tank top that clings to his sculpted chest. Beads of sweat trace the contours of his arms and shoulders, catching the harsh overhead gym lighting. His veins are visible along his forearms from exertion. The background shows industrial gym equipment in soft focus, with mirrors reflecting his determined expression. The lighting is dramatic and directional, emphasizing every muscle definition and the raw physicality of the moment."
            },
            {
                "role": "user",
                "content": "Refine, expand and improve this prompt with more visual details and better structure: \"dancer on stage\""
            },
            {
                "role": "assistant",
                "content": "Framed from a low angle looking up toward the stage lights, a graceful dancer is captured mid-performance in an elaborate costume that accentuates her lithe, flexible body in an elegant arabesque. The form-fitting outfit highlights her slender waist and long, toned legs extended in a perfect line. Sequins and beadwork catch the colorful stage lights as her arms extend gracefully, muscles defined beneath the fabric. Her expression conveys intense emotion and artistic passion. Dramatic theatrical lighting creates bold shadows that emphasize her body's lines and the fluidity of movement frozen in time."
            },
            {
                "role": "user",
                "content": "Refine, expand and improve this prompt with more visual details and better structure: \"couple walking in rain\""
            },
            {
                "role": "assistant",
                "content": "Framed from a medium shot at eye level with a warm three-quarter angle, a couple walks arm-in-arm down a rain-slicked city street at night. She tucks close to him beneath a shared black umbrella, her red coat a vivid splash against the grey surroundings. He holds the umbrella with one hand and her waist with the other, their steps synchronized on the glistening pavement. Neon shop signs reflect in the puddles as streaks of pink and blue. Rain falls in visible sheets through the glow of a nearby streetlight. Their faces are half-lit, smiling at some shared joke, breath visible in the cold night air."
            }
        ]
    },
    "expand_text": {
        "display_name": "Expand Text",
        "instruction_template": "Expand on the following text with more details, examples, and vivid descriptions while keeping the same core meaning: \"{prompt}\"",
        "examples": [
            {
                "role": "user",
                "content": "Expand on the following text with more details, examples, and vivid descriptions while keeping the same core meaning: \"The swimmer dove into the pool.\""
            },
            {
                "role": "assistant",
                "content": "The athletic swimmer stood poised at the edge of the pool, her toned muscles tense with anticipation, water droplets still glistening on her bronzed skin from her warm-up. In one fluid motion, her lean body arced gracefully through the air, arms extended overhead, fingertips leading the way. She sliced into the crystal-clear water with barely a splash, her streamlined form gliding beneath the surface as bubbles trailed along her sculpted shoulders and back. The cool water enveloped her completely as she began her powerful underwater dolphin kicks."
            },
            {
                "role": "user",
                "content": "Expand on the following text with more details, examples, and vivid descriptions while keeping the same core meaning: \"The model posed for the camera.\""
            },
            {
                "role": "assistant",
                "content": "The model positioned herself before the camera with practiced ease, shifting her weight onto one hip to accentuate the curve of her waist. She tilted her chin slightly upward, allowing the studio lights to sculpt shadows along her defined cheekbones and the graceful line of her neck. Her slender arms moved fluidly as she transitioned between poses, each movement highlighting different aspects of her lithe figure. The photographer captured the way the fabric draped across her body, how her long legs seemed to extend endlessly, and the confident arch of her back that spoke of years of professional experience."
            },
            {
                "role": "user",
                "content": "Expand on the following text with more details, examples, and vivid descriptions while keeping the same core meaning: \"The fighter trained hard.\""
            },
            {
                "role": "assistant",
                "content": "The fighter pushed through another grueling training session, sweat streaming down his face and soaking through his compression shirt. His muscular arms burned with each repetition as he pounded the heavy bag, veins bulging along his forearms with every devastating strike. His core contracted rhythmically with his breathing, visible proof of countless hours of conditioning. Scars from previous bouts marked his knuckles and eyebrow, badges of honor in his brutal profession. He shadowboxed in front of the mirror, watching his powerful shoulders roll with each combination, his entire physique a weapon honed through relentless dedication."
            },
            {
                "role": "user",
                "content": "Expand on the following text with more details, examples, and vivid descriptions while keeping the same core meaning: \"She got ready for the evening.\""
            },
            {
                "role": "assistant",
                "content": "She stood before the full-length mirror in her softly lit bedroom, carefully applying the final touches to her makeup. She held up two dresses on hangers, tilting her head at each option before selecting the emerald green one that brought out her eyes. She stepped into it, smoothing the fabric over her hips as it hugged her figure elegantly. Her fingers fastened a delicate gold necklace at her throat, and she swept her hair into a loose updo that left a few tendrils framing her face. The mirror reflected back a woman transformed — poised, radiant, and ready for whatever the evening might bring."
            },
            {
                "role": "user",
                "content": "Expand on the following text with more details, examples, and vivid descriptions while keeping the same core meaning: \"He waited for her at the restaurant.\""
            },
            {
                "role": "assistant",
                "content": "He sat at a corner table in the candlelit restaurant, adjusting his tie for the third time and checking his watch. The table was set for two with crisp white linens, polished silverware, and a single red rose in a slender vase. He straightened the napkin on her side of the table, then leaned back in his chair, drumming his fingers on the armrest. Through the window he could see the rain-glossed street outside, headlights sweeping past in bright arcs. When the front door finally opened and he caught sight of her silhouette in the entrance, he rose immediately, a broad smile replacing the nervous tension in his jaw."
            }
        ]
    },
